	<sentence id="s2" text="Over 60 years after the initial description of PDE, we report the first animal model for this disease: an aldh7a1-null zebrafish (li>Danio rerio</i>) displaying deficient lysine metabolism and spontaneous and recurrent seizures in the larval stage (10 days postfertilization).">
